import React from 'react' import States from 'C:/MY_PROJECT/final/src/rawData/states.json' import { useState } from 'react' import { useEffect } from 'react' import axios from 'axios' const ModifyNgo = () => { var states = States const [ngoData, setNgoData] = useState([]) var url = "http://localhost:400/NgoDetailsControllerImpl/selectByStateId/AP" useEffect(() => { axios.get(url) .then(resp => setNgoData(resp)) }) return (
{ngoData[0]}
) } export default ModifyNgo
